metadata.name: 100 Dollars "American Platinum Eagle" Bullion
metadata.description:
Commemorative issue First Amendment to the United States Constitution - Freedom of Speech

Obverse A branch from a juvenile oak tree.

Script: Latin

Lettering: WITH FREEDOM OF SPEECH LIBERTY BLOSSOMS IN GOD WE TRUST E PLURIBUS UNUM 2022

Translation: With Freedom of Speech Liberty Blossoms In God we Trust Out of many, one
